data.description: This two-story, end unit townhome features a kitchen with a large pantry and island, white cabinetry and granite counter tops, a half bath and family room that overlooks a covered lanai. Upstairs, you'll find 2 secondary bedrooms with a full bath and a spacious master suite with a walk-in closet and double-sink vanity bathroom. The laundry area is also on the second floor for added convenience.
